se xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 28, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wbm1665703011575.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wbm1665703011575.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wbm1665703011575.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wbm1665703011575\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $stripattributes\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wbm1665703011575___stripattributes_291049\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the result of removing character attributes, frames, and rulers from a string.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__topic_d89849e1_d89850e1_d89851e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__p_d89852e1_d89853e1_d89854e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$stripattributes</span> (<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>)</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__topic_d59777e1_d59778e1_d59779e1_d59780e1_d59781e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1194482e69\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__table_d9740e1_d9741e1_d9742e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__table_d9740e1_d9741e1_d9742e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__table_d9740e1_d9741e1_d9742e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__table_d9740e1_d9741e1_d9742e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wbm1665703011575__table_d9740e1_d9741e1_d9742e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wbm1665703011575__table_d9740e1_d9741e1_d9742e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wbm1665703011575__table_d9740e1_d9741e1_d9742e1__entry__3\">\n String, field, variable, or a function that evaluates to a string.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__topic_d59782e1_d59783e1_d59784e1_d59785e1_d59786e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1194482e123\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__p_d89861e1_d89862e1_d89863e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> with character attributes, frames, and ruler removed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__topic_d59787e1_d59788e1_d59789e1_d59790e1_d59791e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1194482e135\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__topic_d59792e1_d59793e1_d59794e1_d59795e1_d59796e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1194482e145\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__p_d89873e1_d89874e1_d89875e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$stripattributes</span> function returns the result of removing character attributes (bold, italic, and underline), frames, and rulers from <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__note_w2471ab1b7c11b5_w2472ab1b7c11_w2473ab1b7_w2474ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Characters that are not known in the target character set are not stripped from the string, unlike the behavior in Uniface 8 in which they were stripped.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__section_vkv_hbj_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1194482e163\">Example: Stripping Character Attributes from a Field</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following ProcScript example shows how you can strip character\n               attributes from a Unifield, so the text can be used in field EDITBOX:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wbm1665703011575__pre_o53_3bj_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">MYFIELD = \"aaabbb\"\nEDITBOX = $stripattributes(MYFIELD) ; EDITBOX contains \"aaabbb\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/byz1665703006730.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$bold</a><p>Apply the bold character attribute to a string.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xsb1665703008136.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$italic</a><p>Apply the italic character attribute to a string in a Unifield.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wul1665702617735.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$underline</a><p>Return the result of applying the underline character attribute to a string.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgf1665702617809.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>stripattributes</a><p>Remove character attributes, frames, and rulers from Source and put the result in Target.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533282\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533282\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$stripattributes Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 28, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $stripattributes Return the result of removing character attributes, frames, and rulers from a string. $stripattributes ( String ) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description String String String, field, variable, or a function that evaluates to a string. Return Values String with character attributes, frames, and ruler removed. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The $stripattributes function returns the result of removing character attributes (bold, italic, and underline), frames, and rulers from String . Note: Characters that are not known in the target character set are not stripped from the string, unlike the behavior in Uniface 8 in which they were stripped. Example: Stripping Character Attributes from a Field The following ProcScript example shows how you can strip character attributes from a Unifield, so the text can be used in field EDITBOX: MYFIELD = \"aaabbb\" EDITBOX = $stripattributes(MYFIELD) ; EDITBOX contains \"aaabbb\" Copy Related Links $bold Apply the bold character attribute to a string. $italic Apply the italic character attribute to a string in a Unifield. $underline Return the result of applying the underline character attribute to a string. stripattributes Remove character attributes, frames, and rulers from Source and put the result in Target. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}